Package: optimumtt
Type: Package
Title: A colection of functions to help cyclists.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Natan Freitas Leite
Maintainer: Natan Freitas Leite <natanfl@hotmail.com>
Description: A colection of functions to calculate the speed that a cyclist
    will develop, on a given location and climate.
    The main purpose is to give foundation to optimize a timetrial event.
    Another set of functions allow to calculate metrics based on training, such as
    PMax, Wbal and mFTP.
License: GNU v3.0
Imports:
    darksky,
    weathermetrics,
    zoo,
    lubridate,
    changepoint
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
